J_" href="/contact-us/"><span class="Header_ctaButtonText__2sN9X">Get In Touch</span></a><button class="Header_mobileMenuToggle__VdtR4" aria-label="Toggle mobile menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button></div></nav></div></div></header><main style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:70vh;text-align:center;padding:40px 20px;background-color:#f8f9fa"><div style="margin-bottom:30px;max-width:300px;width:100%"><img alt="404 - Page Not Found" width="300" height="200" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent;width:100%;height:auto" src="/images/404.svg"/></div><h1 style="font-size:72px;font-weight:700;color:#050748;margin:0 0 10px 0;line-height:1">404</h1><h2 style="font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:#333;margin:0 0 15px 0">Page Not Found</h2><p style="font-size:16px;color:#666;max-width:500px;margin:0 0 30px 0;line-height:1.6">Sorry, the page you are looking for doesn&#x27;t exist or has been moved. Please check the URL or navigate back to our homepage.</p><a style="display:inline-block;background-color:#e77625;color:#ffffff;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;transition:background-color 0.3s ease" href="/">Back to Homepage</a><div style="margin-top:30px;display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center"><a style="color:#050748;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px" href="/contact-us/">Contact Us</a><a style="color:#050748;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px" href="/company-overview/">About Us</a><a style="color:#050748;text-decoration:underline;font-size:14px" href="/careers/">Careers</a></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><footer class="Footer_footer__uARCH" data-site-footer="true" style="--tj-ff-heading:var(--font-poppins), &#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif;--tj-ff-body:var(--font-poppins), &#x27;Poppins&#x27;, sans-serif"><div class="Footer_footerRow2__AuvDQ"><div class="Footer_footerContainer__PBHsr"><div class="Footer_footerGrid__v_AZM"><div class="Footer_footerCol__IGVL7"><div class="Footer_ftrBrandPp__sLoLj"><a class="Footer_navbarBrand__aBNsy" href="/"><img alt="ideyaLabs" fetchPriority="low" loading="lazy" width="169" height="40" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Footer_fDarkLogo__J5MCs" style="color:transparent;aspect-ratio:169/40" src="https://d1axmbaf5hvdh0.cloudfront.net/images/ideyaLabs-black-R.webp"/></a></div><p class="Footer_companyDescription__Leias">At ideyaLabs, we empower businesses with services like AI/ML, QA, OTT App Development, Cloud Solutions, and Digital Transformation. Our expertise drives innovation across these domains.</p></div><div class="Footer_footerCol__IGVL7"><h3>Industries</h3><ul class="Footer_footerAddressList__rbFEq"><li><a href="/banking-and-financial-services/">BFSI &amp; Fintech</a></li><li><a href="/healthcare-software-development/">Healthcare</a></li><li><a href="/elearning-software-development-services/">Education</a></li><li><a href="/media-entertainment-software-solutions/">Media &amp; Entertainment</a></li><li><a href="/retail-ecommerce-software-development/">Retail &amp; eCommerce</a></li><li><a href="/logistics-software-development-services/">Transportation &amp; Logistics</a></li><li><a href="/telecom-software-development/">Telecommunication &amp; Wireless</a></li><li><a href="/real-estate-software-development/">Real Estate</a></li><li><a href="/travel-and-hospitality/">Travel &amp; Hospitality</a></li><li><a href="/insurance-software/">Insurance</a></li><li><a href="/energy-management-software-development/">Energy, Resources &amp; Utilities</a></li><li><a href="/automotive-software-development-services/">Automotive</a></li><li><a href="/software-development-in-manufacturing-services/">Manufacturing</a></li></ul></div><div class="Footer_footerCol__IGVL7"><h3>Services</h3><ul class="Footer_footerAddressList__rbFEq"><li><a class="Footer_textDark__c9PLl" href="/ai-development-services/">AI Development Services</a></li><li><a class="Foo